2025-06-05FINCustoms TariffOrder Amending the Ukraine Goods Remission Order Order Amending the UKRAINE GOODS REMISSION ORDER in order to remit customs duties for all goods originating in Ukraine and imported into Canada, with the exception of over-access supply-managed products and anti-dumping and countervailing duties paid or payable under the Special Import Measures Act, from June 10, 2025 to June 9, 2026.Registration: SOR/2025-0135 Publication Date: 2025-06-18
subject: Order Amending the Ukraine Goods Remission Order
precis: Order Amending the UKRAINE GOODS REMISSION ORDER in order to remit customs duties for all goods originating in Ukraine and imported into Canada, with the exception of over-access supply-managed products and anti-dumping and countervailing duties paid or payable under the Special Import Measures Act, from June 10, 2025 to June 9, 2026.
